TopicTitle: KSP Crashing exclusively in the VAB/SPH seemingly random

Articles.Content:
I am experiencing problems with KSP, the game seems to be crashing only in the SPH and VAB when constructing rockets and seems to do so when I either delete or select a part, the game runs just fine outside of these 2 places and works when I am launching vessels. 

I can recreate the problem by doing the following:

1. Put your cursor over the parts list in the VAB 

2. Select a part

3. Press that same part as so it deletes itself, do this rapidly and it will crash after about 30 seconds.

I run the 64 bit version of KSP and use the following mods:

-Module Manager

-Mechjeb

-Chatterer

-TriggerTech (Kerbal Alarm Clock)

-EVE

 

 

System specs:

Processor: Intel(R) Core(TM) i5-4210U

CPU @ 1.70GHz 2.40 GHz

Installed memory (RAM): 8.00 GB

System Type: 64-bit Operating System,

x64- based processor
